Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.10,0:00:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这么痛苦的回忆的话 我将不再向他人渴求什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.04,0:00:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十六岁的冬天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.97,0:00:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我体验了能撕裂身心的痛苦离别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.48,0:01:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}白色花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.16,0:02:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又到圣诞节了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.87,0:02:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与栞的初次相遇是在春天的某一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.72,0:02:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天早晨 我比平常早了很多地来到了学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.32,0:02:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中二年级的我对什么都感到厌烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.94,0:02:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是这个宛如天使牧场的学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.35,0:02:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是带着纯真微笑的学生们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.20,0:02:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界一定是正确的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.29,0:02:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就是无法适应它的坏羔羊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.56,0:02:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救这样的我吧 阿门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.27,0:02:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.54,0:02:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非得和大家一起笑不可？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.85,0:02:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非得去听那些毫无兴趣的话题不可？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.71,0:02:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我保持着沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.01,0:02:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连做什么好或是想去做什么也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.83,0:03:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也别碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的事情全部忘掉吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.38,0:03:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的内心中没有一丝的滋润
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.24,0:03:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像一个人困在一片干涸的荒野中无路可走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.97,0:03:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.32,0:03:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着大人样的她 看起来全身充满着我所没有的滋润的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.96,0:03:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久保 栞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.50,0:03:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.48,0:03:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还是第一次听到\n从你嘴里冒出别人的名字来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.00,0:03:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.27,0:03:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是今早认识了一个那样的一年级生而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.95,0:03:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的内心中 有什么东西正在开始变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.23,0:04:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.32,0:04:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣 你作为花蕾的自觉好像太少了一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 有稀客在呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.55,0:04:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.77,0:04:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.13,0:04:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为祥子长得跟日本娃娃一样漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不由自主地就想招待她一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我长得一副洋味十足的脸孔真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 闹别扭了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 我喜欢圣的脸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说也是凭脸孔选的妹妹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.86,0:04:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实不敢当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她曾说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.18,0:04:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“因为我想一直看着这张脸 所以请待在我身边”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.31,0:04:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这一句话 我决定成为她的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.60,0:04:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢这样单纯而明快的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.52,0:04:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 从一开始姐姐对待我的方式就非常地高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.08,0:04:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我变得连自已都吃惊的积极起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.36,0:04:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？ 圣大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.20,0:05:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久保 栞同学今天休假了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.94,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.18,0:05:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概在圣堂那里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.29,0:05:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像理所当然似的栞出现在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.18,0:05:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为被这个世界所爱的洁白而闪耀的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.37,0:05:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安 白蔷薇的花蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.22,0:05:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.31,0:05:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份心情...会让你为难吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.29,0:05:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将自已完全地暴露 追寻着依靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经完全不再有退路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.11,0:05:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直想着要见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.06,0:05:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于在这个学园里能遇见栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想从心里对神说声感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.26,0:06:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在可利用的时间里我们都尽量单独相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.76,0:06:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越来越远离蔷薇馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.32,0:06:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断陷入了栞的那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.89,0:06:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微保持一点距离不是更好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.66,0:06:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果想认妹妹 那到也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.81,0:06:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式地交与念珠 好好地向大家介绍一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.80,0:06:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会考虑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我可以走了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 一定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.26,0:06:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有打算认栞作妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.79,0:06:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐妹的仪式\n是那些没有像征就无法安心的人们做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从心底嘲笑着这一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.45,0:06:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.63,0:06:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.06,0:07:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 我们双方各自都将\n与生俱来的双手连结到了同一个人的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.93,0:07:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个结果就是将其它的东西完全地排除在外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被说了什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.38,0:07:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明仅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了吗？ 游泳的补习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.36,0:07:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在事故中丧失了双亲的栞一直住在学生宿舍里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.16,0:07:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夏天 栞没有回到长崎的叔叔那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.01,0:07:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是留在了东京的某个修道院里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.87,0:08:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时在这里避避雨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.01,0:08:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么关系 擦擦你自已的头发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.95,0:08:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.17,0:08:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.70,0:09:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们 会作为不同的个体出生到这个世上呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.35,0:09:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.78,0:09:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 你再睡一会儿也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了后我会叫醒你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.16,0:09:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.27,0:09:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.82,0:09:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨啊 别停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间就这样停止好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.37,0:09:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想与栞溶为一体然后消失掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.76,0:09:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种心情究竟是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向自已以外的人渴求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条路的前方又是哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.75,0:10:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个答案恐怕永远也找不到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即使这样也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.55,0:10:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最真实的东西只有栞的悸动 体温和吐息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.21,0:10:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这些就是我所期望的这个世界的全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.77,0:10:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的心中栞的存在膨胀得越来越大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.85,0:10:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在蔷薇馆的时间变得越来越少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.89,0:10:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.28,0:10:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.22,0:10:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也想和你一起喝喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.26,0:10:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.56,0:10:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.38,0:11:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断绝与我的姐妹之缘 重新找一个妹妹如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.85,0:11:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.91,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要违反约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.45,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我毕业以前 你可要好好地待在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.05,0:11:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你不认妹妹 那也没什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.80,0:11:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走你自已不会后悔的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.56,0:11:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在等我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摆出那副表情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来就像我是瘟神一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是说教吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微冷静一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.24,0:11:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明对我们的事什么也不知道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.95,0:11:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你又知道栞同学什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“什么”是指...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.84,0:11:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得还是不要陷得太深为好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.91,0:11:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要特意来说这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不想看到你受伤的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.38,0:11:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会受伤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她如果不在了你会怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.92,0:12:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞会...不在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都没听到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.18,0:12:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.83,0:12:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞同学毕业后会进入修道院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.79,0:12:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要成为修女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.71,0:12:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.35,0:12:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.56,0:12:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.69,0:12:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.01,0:12:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在进入这间学校之前就已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要隐瞒到现在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是没有机会说而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.98,0:12:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了也不会有什么改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.91,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然很喜欢栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.81,0:12:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却不喜欢我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.83,0:12:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.12,0:12:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个毕业前的陪伴… 你是这样随便地考虑的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.18,0:13:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会这么喜欢一个人也是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么要成为修女什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.36,0:13:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我 你宁愿选择神吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是只有栞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要抛弃我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.53,0:13:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要像那样逼问我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为修女是我的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么不敢看着我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在迷惑吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.36,0:13:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞 我喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.61,0:13:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.73,0:13:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣母玛莉亚在看着我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是栞的回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.19,0:13:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输给了圣母玛莉亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.11,0:13:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的上课态度变得失常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.07,0:14:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结业式的那天 我受到传唤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.59,0:14:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是栞的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.21,0:14:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她已经再没有什么关系了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.85,0:14:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久保 栞也是这样说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.11,0:14:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是自已的错之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.11,0:14:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞也被叫来这里了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.66,0:14:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一头陷入一样东西中而看不清周围 不是一件很寂寞的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.63,0:14:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞两日前提出了外宿申请 无论在宿舍还是修道院都找不到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.67,0:14:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞 怎样才能见到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.71,0:14:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蔷薇馆会开一个联欢会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.87,0:14:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令会为大家做好吃的饼干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有心情的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.04,0:14:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞 好想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.99,0:15:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想见你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.04,0:15:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.12,0:15:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在见不着你的时候 我只是想着你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.97,0:15:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使做祈祷 也没法让你的样子离开脑海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.57,0:15:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园长非常担心我们的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.61,0:15:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也做过约定不再见面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.15,0:15:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.06,0:15:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞 一起逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.13,0:15:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.13,0:15:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在未知的土地上 不被任何人打扰的活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.96,0:15:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.29,0:15:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.53,0:15:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会不愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和圣在一起 到哪里都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.75,0:16:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.05,0:16:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.73,0:16:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.70,0:16:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾好行李就过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.43,0:16:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在车站等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.44,0:16:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.50,0:16:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.42,0:16:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞微笑着目送我而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.69,0:16:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法忘记那个微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.93,0:16:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.75,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定的时间已过去3小时了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞已经不会来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.06,0:17:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我仍无法离开月台的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.30,0:17:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无法舍弃也许栞\n马上就会从那个楼梯下来的仅有的一点希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.77,0:17:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是做梦 我也想见到栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.16,0:17:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.10,0:17:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.15,0:17:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我代替栞同学来接你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.38,0:17:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞同学好像不会与你一起走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.33,0:17:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞同学好像曾经来过这个车站一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.85,0:17:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从远处注视着在月台上的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.61,0:18:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后觉得果然还是不能这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.96,0:18:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然来了为什么不直接...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见面后会让决心变弱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变弱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她看起来很有大人样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.32,0:18:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但毕竟仍只是高中一年级生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.63,0:18:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会动摇也是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.17,0:18:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞会去哪里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.56,0:18:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 听说会转学到很远的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.39,0:18:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是她接受了的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.00,0:18:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.58,0:18:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有遇见我的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够相遇是件好事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.13,0:18:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能创造可以坦然回想着\n“能够相遇真好”的未来 那么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.87,0:18:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种未来一定无法来临的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.32,0:18:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤痕总有一天会愈合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.84,0:18:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你不是还有我在身边吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.03,0:18:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是真以为我只爱着你的脸孔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.01,0:18:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.63,0:18:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼 那只是为了不增加你负担的一个方便的借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对待你的方式可是很高明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.10,0:19:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.07,0:19:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是姐姐不是就要毕业了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.20,0:19:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会担心你的可不只是我一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.48,0:19:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.29,0:19:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你担心真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.93,0:19:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是令做的饼干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.26,0:19:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.81,0:19:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.02,0:19:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.07,0:19:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.53,0:19:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才已经向圣的母亲打了电话说你要住下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.18,0:19:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闲话少说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.47,0:19:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从明天开始就是开心的寒假了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.14,0:19:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就玩到深夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.38,0:19:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安安静静地闹它一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.46,0:19:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日期已经变了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.13,0:19:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.59,0:19:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.02,0:20:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞前夜过去 我知道自己已是十七岁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.45,0:20:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.46,0:20:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.59,0:20:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.05,0:20:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人也来帮忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.65,0:20:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.71,0:20:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日诚子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 也就是须加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.32,0:20:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去大波斯菊编缉部时 曾见过面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.44,0:20:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.45,0:20:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉前段时间失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.72,0:20:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.52,0:20:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的学生给您添了不少麻烦真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.60,0:20:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.04,0:20:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是佐藤 圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 今天是...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.44,0:21:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来见学园长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.42,0:21:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那么 我来为您带路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我知道路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.96,0:21:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟过去一点也没变啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.12,0:21:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.47,0:21:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉安的毕业生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.13,0:21:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 据说已知道香织还活着的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.51,0:21:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是要在圣诞前夜去见香织的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.81,0:21:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就是说香织在这里了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也许是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 去见学园长是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.45,0:21:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 是这样啊 学园长就是香织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.75,0:21:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么两个人在隔了这么多年后终于可以再见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.71,0:21:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.54,0:21:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联欢会要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.49,0:21:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.74,0:21:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.05,0:21:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.56,0:21:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.54,0:22:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.58,0:22:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.39,0:22:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是我的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.14,0:22:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Happy Birthday
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.25,0:23:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从波折的姐妹宣言开始 终于到了现在这个时候
